Herladen.

1565
02:33:31.334 --> 02:33:32.734
Kijk uit.

1566
02:34:05.016 --> 02:34:06.323
Ja. Jake.

1567
02:34:06.449 --> 02:34:07.849
Bro. kijk.

1568
02:34:36.315 --> 02:34:37.933
Jake.

1569
02:34:41.723 --> 02:34:43.123
De Asmensen.

1570
02:34:43.409 --> 02:34:46.386
Vijand in zicht. Banshee-rijders.
Meer dan 100.

1571
