1593
02:36:49.823 --> 02:36:51.223
Kom op.

1594
02:37:04.386 --> 02:37:07.372
Al-Moeder. hoor mijn woorden aan.

1595
02:37:08.623 --> 02:37:10.176
Alstublieft. help ons.

1596
02:37:11.366 --> 02:37:12.766
Ik smeek u.

1597
02:37:13.335 --> 02:37:15.597
U bent onze enige hoop.

1598
02:37:28.686 --> 02:37:31.394
