Niet doen.

1601
02:37:41.222 --> 02:37:43.639
Nee. alstublieft.

1602
02:37:55.471 --> 02:37:57.491
Apenkop.
- Vooruit.

1603
02:37:58.355 --> 02:38:00.075
Kom op.

1604
02:38:01.792 --> 02:38:03.192
Kom.

1605
